print("=== PARAM FILE: asg_model_pc_v14.param ===")
print("=== Changes vs v13: ===")
print("  1. nlive 50 -> 100 (via shell), num_repeats 58 -> 29 — same wall-clock, 2x ndead")
print("  2. chi0 prior [1.50,9.00] -> [2.80,6.50] (PC v13 posterior: 4.73±0.42, 3.5σ)")
print("  3. mu   prior [0.50,10.0] -> [3.00,6.10] (PC v13 posterior: 4.54±0.31, 3.5σ)")
print("  4. grade_frac [2,5] -> [1,8] — halve slow CLASS calls cost, more nuisance mixing")
print("  5. precision_criterion 0.01 -> 0.005 — stops a bit later (10-15% more ndead)")
print("  Net expected: ~same runtime, 2x nequals (500+ vs 261), ln(Z) ~ -1407 (+2.5 Occam)")

